text: Was really looking forward to this one and it turned out so mediocre and bland that it felt like a huge waste of time. The problem is that you have two very charismatic, colorful guys and somehow they don't have anything decent to work with because of poor story and really generic plus uninteresting dialogue. What makes these guys especially Jackson great in some movies is that he is given cool character to work with . You can't just give him couple of motherfucker lines and expect it to be good. Other thing is that it is tonally conflicting, oversaturated and unnecessary long with story arc they could completely eliminate and the movie would gain points. It is never exciting as it wants to be or funny as it think it is. In the end very dissatisfying and forgettable film.
